  psych_school_psychoanalysis_desc: "Uncover the influence of the unconscious, defenses, and the symbolic language of dreams.",
  psych_school_jungian_desc: "Explore archetypes, the collective unconscious, and the journey toward individuation.",
  psych_school_object_relations_desc: "Examine how early relationships with 'objects' (others) shape our internal world.",
